data.description: This conveniently located property features panoramic mountain and valley views with a 2600 square foot, 40x60 finished shop.  Charming farmhouse style offers a front porch that extends the full length of the house.  Upstairs is solely a private master suite with a huge walk in closet plus a deck off the bedroom. 1.85 acres of property offers limitless potential and opportunity for parking RV's and other toys. There are 3 additional bedrooms and and one and half baths on the ground floor.
